Package com.gmail.mohitsainiknl2.mscalculator.theme

Interface Theme

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultTheme
public interface Theme
Theme interface help to guide the program to make a new Theme for this Calculator. Note :- if one need to add new Color in color-plate, then, one have to add the declaration of this color's getter-method in this Interface.
